headline: Invitation Homes Announces Dates for Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: DALLAS, October 06, 2025--Invitation Homes Inc. (NYSE: INVH) ("Invitation Homes" or the "Company"), the nation's premier single-family home leasing and management company, will release its third quarter 2025 financial and operating results on Wednesday, October 29, 2025, after the market closes.
